<TEXT>
police arrested five men suspected in the 
assassination of luis carlos galan the presidential hopeful whose 
slaying caused a government crackdown on colombias notorious drug 
traffickers 
also tuesday police said they had begun proceedings to extradite 
the reputed finance chief of the medellin drug cartel to the united 
states where he faces conspiracy and drug trafficking charges 
colombian newspapers meanwhile reported today the arrest of an 
