want bad publicity 
jeri laber executive director of helsinki watch in new york 
suggested the kremlin simply is less concerned about activists 
influence somebody there has realized its not so bad when these 
people speak out 
a soviet embassy spokesman in washington said only that kremlim 
policy on visas for travel to the west doesnt discriminate between 
activists and all other soviet travelers whose total number could 
reach 2 million this year 
